title: P.F. Chang's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Veggie friendly chain bistro/restaurant with a trendy atmosphere. Caters to vegan and other special diets and reportedly uses separate cooking utensils and prep areas for the veg food. Will substitute tofu for meat in most dishes. Extensive menu with vegetarian suitable items marked.
